data.name: CtorAnalyserTitle
data.value: CtorSet should only be used in specific circumstances

data.name: CtorBridgeAttributeMessageFormat
data.value: CtorSet's propertyRetriever lambda must directly indicate an instance property that has no Bridge attributes on the getter or setter

data.name: CtorDirectPropertyTargetAccessorArgumentMessageFormat
data.value: CtorSet's propertyRetriever lambda must directly indicate an instance property with a getter and a setter (which may be private)

data.name: CtorMayOnlyBeCalledWithConstructorMessageFormat
data.value: CtorSet should only be called within a constructor

data.name: CtorSimpleMemberAccessRuleMessageFormat
data.value: CtorSet must be a simple member access expression that targets "this" - it must be of the form this.CtorSet(..)

data.name: CtorSimplePropertyAccessorArgumentMessageFormat
data.value: CtorSet's propertyRetriever lambda must directly indicate an instance property with a getter and a setter (which may be private)

data.name: GetPropertyAnalyserTitle

data.name: GetPropertyBridgeAttributeMessageFormat

data.name: GetPropertyDirectPropertyTargetAccessorArgumentMessageFormat
data.value: GetProperty's propertyRetriever lambda's target must be a direct access and may not include any casts or other indirection

data.name: GetPropertySimplePropertyAccessorArgumentMessageFormat

data.name: IAmImmutablePropertiesMustHaveSettersMessageFormat

data.name: IAmImmutablePropertiesMustNotHaveBridgeAttributesMessageFormat
